agent (depth 1/2). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: You are senior-backend. Test Module 1: AUTH API for ahv-dtlx-backend.\n\n## Context\n- Workspace: /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend\n- Server port: 5555\n- Label: dtlx:auth-test\n\n## Steps\n\n### 1. Setup\n- cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend\n- cp .env.example .env  (if .env doesn't exist)\n- Run: yarn seed  (seeds admin account admin123@gmail.com / 123456)\n- Start server: yarn dev  (background)\n- Wait for server to start (look for \"listening\" or \"started\")\n\n### 2. Test AUTH endpoints (PUBLIC - no token needed)\nUse curl to test each endpoint:\n\n```\nPOST /api/v1/auth/login\nBody: { \"email\": \"admin123@gmail.com\", \"password\": \"123456\" }\nExpected: JWT token\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/register  \nBody: { \"email\": \"test@test.com\", \"password\": \"123456\", \"name\": \"Test User\" }\nExpected: user created\n\nGET /api/v1/auth/me\nExpected: current user info (if authenticated)\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/forgot-password\nBody: { \"email\": \"admin123@gmail.com\" }\n\nPOST /api/v1/auth/refresh\n```\n\n### 3. After login success\n- Save the JWT token from login response\n- Test GET /api/v1/auth/me with the token (Authorization: Bearer <token>)\n\n### 4. Report\nFor EACH endpoint, report:\n- вң… /api/v1/auth/xxx вҖ” HTTP status, response (truncated if long)\n- вқҢ /api/v1/auth/xxx вҖ” HTTP status, error message\n\n## Rules\n- Read-only API testing\n- NEVER push or commit code\n- Kill background server when done"}],"timestamp":1776131231850,"__openclaw":{"id":"4b8eb889","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776131231877,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"5afe1e66","seq":2}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1776131239731,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"55a05b1d","seq":3}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:e3ca11a2-c1e6-4d1d-9d7c-680d2d0d259a","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","label":"dtlx:api-test","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-dtlx-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776131199486,"sessionId":"b91b97c7-6c79-42e5-82db-f0fe613820a3","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":13326,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"killed","startedAt":1776130995085,"endedAt":1776131198083,"runtimeMs":120587,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":true,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/b91b97c7-6c79-42e5-82db-f0fe613820a3.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The seed command doesn't exist. Let me check the package.json for available scripts."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rp80wdcy1t2g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat package.json | grep -A 30 '\"scripts\"'","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":141,"output":83,"totalTokens":13409,"cacheRead":12917,"cacheWrite":268,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776131191078,"responseId":"062ccf78fa2ef02cf530584ff3ea9ac7","__openclaw":{"id":"726c10f3","seq":17}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"ant