ing covers the day and sets up for Tuesday.\n\n\nNow I'll format this as a status report."},{"type":"text","text":"рҹҢ… **ORBIS MORNING BRIEFING**\nрҹ“… Monday, April 13, 2026\nвҸ° 10:00 PM UTC | 5:00 AM UTC+7\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n\n**1пёҸвғЈ YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED TASKS**\n\nвң… **AHV Works Review** вҖ” FULL REVIEW COMPLETE (commit 84cdb2d)\nвң… **Session Recovery** вҖ” Crash at 00:34 UTC (HTTP 500 / context overflow), fully recovered on model `AHV-Holding-DEV`\nвң… **FE Sync** вҖ” Frontend fully synchronized with remote develop вң…\nвң… **DTLX/QLHV Systems** вҖ” Stable, shared DB architecture operational\nвң… **34-Agent Ecosystem** вҖ” SKILL_GATES, HANDOVER/FEEDBACK, OPENSPEC all verified вң…\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n\n**2пёҸвғЈ TODAY'S PRIORITIES**\n\nрҹ”ҙ **P0 вҖ” AHV Works Fixes** вҖ” 13 unresolved P0 issues queued for resolution\nрҹҹЎ **Stitch MCP Wrapper** вҖ” Complete integration testing post-gateway restart\nрҹҹЎ **stitch-connect Skill** вҖ” Update to use MCP wrapper (replacing OAuth flow)\nрҹ”ө **BE Notification System** вҖ” Local behind remote by 11 commits; notification system feature pending merge\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n\n**3пёҸвғЈ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\n\nвҡ пёҸ **BE Merge Conflict** вҖ” Backend is 11 commits behind remote on `notification-system`; remote is 2 commits ahead on `data-isolation`. **Lead decision required** before merge can proceed.\n\nвҡ пёҸ **Context Overflow Risk** вҖ” Session crash root cause identified (200k+ tokens / model instability). Monitor session health closely.\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n\n**Pipeline Status:** рҹҹў HEALTHY\n**Active Agents:** 34 (v4 ecosystem)\n**Active Session:** telegram:group:-5212380728\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\nOrbis рҹҢҗ вҖ” Global Orchestrator"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvhold