re\n\n**DTLX vГ  QLHV lГ  2 hб»Ү thб»‘ng DГҷNG CHUNG database:**\n\n```\nDTLX (MASTER) в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ QLHV (SUBSYSTEM)\n   Hб»Ү thб»‘ng chГӯnh                    TГЎch ra cho THбәҰY/GV\n   Ban giГЎm Д‘б»‘c, Sales, Admin        GiГЎo viГӘn quбәЈn lГҪ HV\n        в”Ӯ                                 в”Ӯ\n        в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ SHARED MONGODB в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n              103.253.21.98:27017\n```\n\n**вҶ’ QLHV phбәЈi Д‘б»“ng bб»ҷ dб»Ҝ liб»Үu vб»ӣi DTLX luГҙn luГҙn.**\n**вҶ’ Khi dev QLHV, phбәЈi HIб»ӮU DTLX schema vГ¬ cГ№ng DB.**\n\n## Project Identity\n- **DTLX Name**: AHV DTLX (ДҗГ o TбәЎo LГЎi Xe) вҖ” MASTER\n- **QLHV Name**: AHV QLHV (QuбәЈn LГҪ Hб»Қc ViГӘn) вҖ” SUBSYSTEM\n- **Telegram\n\nSource: memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46","source":"memory","citation":"memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"6d33dcbcde98902d6f184f316670fd98825cd1bfa92d0d558a8ab236984c0dee","path":"memory/dtlx-context.md","startLine":38,"endLine":60,"score":0.7177166514550428,"textScore":0.7177166514550428,"snippet":"### Bб»ҷ 2: Ecosystem (ahv-qlhv/*) вҖ” ДҗANG DEV TRONG SESSION NГҖY\n- `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be` (id: 81078323) вҖ” Last: 2026-04-11 вң…\n- `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe` (id: 81078350) вҖ” Last: 2026-04-11 вң…\n- Дҗang hoбәЎt Д‘б»ҷng: develop + main\n\n### Landing Page (khГҙng Д‘б»Қc)\n- `ahv-dtlx/ahv-landing-page-v2` (id: 80400174)\n\n## Local Workspace (QLHV вҖ” Д‘ang dev)\n- **BE**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/`\n- **FE**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/`\n\n## Database\n- **MongoDB**: `mongodb://103.253.21.98:27017` (SHARED vб»ӣi DTLX)\n- **ERD**: Confluence page `23494657` (v35) вҖ” 20+ entities\n\n## Agents\n- Use prefix `ahv-dtlx:` for all spawned subagents\n\nSource: memory/dtlx-context.md#L38-L60","source":"memory","citation":"memory/dtlx-context.md#L38-L60","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"518063e3e9cd5341c81c75ff2fda15067